{"tid":689701,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"輕鬆吹水打機Group","createTime":"2018-06-04T09:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T12:03:32.000Z","uid":67836,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0cee5b6603b80f4168baa4f2384b5c0441565ad0","tid":689701,"uid":67836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:28:10.000Z","msg":"[無圖]輕鬆打機吹水 TG + Discord Group<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/G32DDuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FG32DDuk.jpg&h=3aa76c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地主要係7點後先上線，平時主要係扮工吹水Group<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">希望大家熱情d 講多d野 唔洗怕羞 唔好咩都唔講 hi下都好<br />\n仲有想大家多D入DISCORD 咁先會容易搵到人打機 <br />\n就算唔打機 吹下水都可以好開心</span></span><br />\n會玩既遊戲有好多種類 Steam Game PC PS4 Switch<br />\n我地依家會主力Steam Game<br />\n多數係合作類 我地有位熱心既巴打整左個List<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我地依家用埋Parsec，<br />\n可以一齊玩一定單機多人(例如Overcooked)既遊戲，<br />\n大家如果有興趣既 歡迎隨時加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一部份我地集體玩過既Game：<br />\n<br />\nLOL 唔使多講 我地會打內戰 NG RANK <br />\n但主要係玩得開心 如果太認真會失去左個樂趣 <br />\n笑下玩下鳩野 比羸更加重要<br />\n<br />\nGarry&rsquo;s Mod<br />\n依隻GAME既玩法有好多 自由度好高 玩家可以自行去STEAM<br />\n既工作坊玩佢地自創既地圖 例如TTT 就係隱藏自己殺手既身份不停去殺人<br />\n加上係咁制造混亂同埋講大話去令到平民同警察內訌 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fTw3bZT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfTw3bZT.jpg&h=2573d10f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vjqBT81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvjqBT81.jpg&h=e1bcd1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHuman: Fall Flat 八人<br />\n一隻合作過關既遊戲 畫風好有趣 D人好似泥膠<br />\n玩落會好有喜感 不自覺咁覺得好好笑 <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p0MxFn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp0MxFn5.jpg&h=5714c482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XEZiRmW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXEZiRmW.jpg&h=9c0cc812&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n玩到拍埋片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iPNVCSGuu9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiPNVCSGuu9s&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d20f8675\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iPNVCSGuu9s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sidFqyKcG4Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsidFqyKcG4Q&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=73c2df03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sidFqyKcG4Q</a><br />\n<br />\nHeroes of Hammerwatch 不限人數<br />\n遊戲目標基本上就係一直前進，打低最後既BOSS，<br />\n每一關都有四層，第四層就係BOSS戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊戲過程會拎到一啲裝備，但Gameover之後，依啲裝備會無晒，但人物lv會keep住。<br />\n如果你中途死左既話，救你既人既靈魂就會同你連埋，<br />\n其中一個人死既話，其他連結左既人就會一齊死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以最後一個人死，就會全部人一次過死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8xqbB0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8xqbB0Q.jpg&h=78da1c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c8tyaon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fc8tyaon.jpg&h=ed7c3e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8lAowK3_58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw8lAowK3_58&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7b4c5697\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8lAowK3_58</a><br />\n<br />\nDeceit 六人<br />\n四人做人，二人做鬼，<br />\n人類要逃出，鬼要殺晒所有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日頭既時候，鬼會維持住人既樣，<br />\n鬼要吸地圖上面既血包，吸足夠血既鬼可以係夜晚變成真正既鬼，一擊秒殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吸血既人一定係鬼，於是乎，鬼可以係人類面前吸血，跟住大叫見到個個人類係吸血既鬼&hellip;<br />\n地圖上仲有唔同既道具，例如直接去睇對方既身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地之前無CAP開圖，後補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ewxzII4Xcew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DewxzII4Xcew&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=19e6b19f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ewxzII4Xcew</a><br />\n<br />\nAlien Swarm: Reactive Drop 八人<br />\n八人合作既L4D2，可以一槍秒殺隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有大量玩家自創地圖<br />\n我地之前無CAP開圖，後補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8Y91cbSjoM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv8Y91cbSjoM&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ac9da84c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8Y91cbSjoM</a><br />\n<br />\nDota2 / War3 地圖<br />\n自訂地圖 守城 溜冰 次次玩都笑到收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地之前無CAP開圖，後補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNo more room in hell <br />\n一隻高難度既打喪屍GAME，無準星，玩家被咬後都會被感染，慢慢變成喪屍，<br />\n需要大家合作過關逃生<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8QC0sWFtass\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8QC0sWFtass&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dd6a59f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8QC0sWFtass</a><br />\n<br />\nECO<br />\n係一隻玩econ, law, technology既game, <br />\n背景係講緊有粒腎石撞緊落地球, 玩定要係粒腎石到之前將時代推進, 發展科技阻止佢。<br />\n但係你有機會因為工業化破壞環境而令到地球毀滅先。<br />\n每個玩家都要揀一條專精既技能升級上去，例如建築技能等等，要玩家分工合作先有可能生存到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fjoF-qLvVY&amp;t=961s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6fjoF-qLvVY%26t%3D961s&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=06dd8dae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fjoF-qLvVY&amp;t=961s</a><br />\n<br />\nRaft\t\t<br />\n一隻海上生存遊戲，要靠海上既漂浮物去獲取資源，或許去海底自己搵，<br />\n但係海上有好多鯊魚會攻擊你，慢慢研發科技進行反擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KTutxuWCnBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKTutxuWCnBI&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2c33558c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KTutxuWCnBI</a>"},{"pid":"855e4a8593c0b1bc5e00f96dde7b1508fcd604a1","tid":689701,"uid":67836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"各色各類既RPG <br />\n如果你有咩想玩既 都可以係GP到找人一齊玩<br />\n我地都好樂意買GAME一齊玩 因為本身大部份人係上班族 所以有一定既經濟能力<br />\n唔洗怕要買GAME就無人陪你玩<br />\n<br />\nGame List <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TTvXkKV7v96s7ogod9YCMb95xMuVeXum80n3EgSUcfg/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1TTvXkKV7v96s7ogod9YCMb95xMuVeXum80n3EgSUcfg%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c36cc173\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TTvXkKV7v96s7ogod9YCMb95xMuVeXum80n3EgSUcfg/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣 歡迎入坑TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EiJC2hMM_HrVp7QQr_BJuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEiJC2hMM_HrVp7QQr_BJuA&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=93121ffa\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EiJC2hMM_HrVp7QQr_BJuA</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：最近研究緊 火影守城，巨魔同寵物小精靈惡魔圈 不可能的boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人探究緊total war <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAoe 3 我地夜晚會打內戰 個個新手<br />\n過多排會一齊玩poe <br />\n現在有8-10人左右長期玩ECO<br />\n<br />\n太多GAME 不能盡錄<br />\n試到有新既GAME好玩 會再分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d75224e1bfbc64675c96eacf2933d6417e27cf","tid":689701,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"好似好多野玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}